00:00:01.160 --> 00:00:12.490
 Pickled cucumber soup with potatoes. I apologize for slipping in the dialogue 

00:00:12.720 --> 00:00:19.530
 of course, no beetroots. Ingredients for 5 liters soup - 10 people. 

00:00:19.700 --> 00:00:26.430
 Vegetable decoction 3100 ml or meat. Pickled cucumbers 500 g. 

00:00:26.580 --> 00:00:34.120
 Butter - oil 80 g. Flour 60 g. 

00:00:34.290 --> 00:00:40.970
 30% cream 300-500 ml. Green dill 20 g. 

00:00:41.190 --> 00:00:47.010
 Cumin, salt, pepper. Water-acid from cucumbers 300 ml. 

00:00:47.190 --> 00:00:51.810
 Potatoes 1400-2000 g. Manner of production: 

00:00:51.950 --> 00:01:05.270
 Pickled cucumbers grate or mix - 

00:01:05.460 --> 00:01:23.560
 stew in butter. Cook the peeled vegetables on vegetable broth 

00:01:23.700 --> 00:01:58.100
 diced potatoes. When the potatoes are soft combine with 

00:01:58.260 --> 00:02:48.750
 stewed cucumbers - topped up when low acidic cucumber. 

00:02:48.900 --> 00:03:05.370
 The whole should be sourdled with scattered flour or without flour. 

00:03:05.450 --> 00:03:41.430
 Let's remember to pour some soup into the cream-beaten and combine with 

00:03:41.550 --> 00:03:50.930
 the remaining soup. Season with salt, pepper, chopped 

00:03:51.080 --> 00:03:59.350
 green dill and possibly add fennel seeds or grated horseradish as you like. 

00:03:59.510 --> 00:04:14.720
 Enjoy your meal. I invite you to culinary films. 

